This project will address absenteeism at a company during work time

Problem:
higher competitiveness 
unachievable business goals 
elevated risk of unemployment 

These factors all increase stress and pressure factors which can become detramental to a persons health.  This could result in minor illness, or a long term condition, for example depression.

Using the data provided i will be conducting a analysis on whether or not a person will be expected to be absent for more than 3 hours in a given work day.

Absenteeism being defined as the following;

Absence from work during normal business hours, resulting in temporary incapacity to execute regular working activity.


